headline: Northern Trust Universe Data: Global Markets Deliver Steady Fourth Quarter Gains to U.S. Institutional Investors
summary: CHICAGO, January 28, 2026--Large U.S. institutional investors had median returns of 2.1% for Q4 2025 and 13.1% for the year, according to the Northern Trust Universe.

headline: Northern Trust Appoints Katie Pries as Country Executive for Canada
summary: TORONTO, January 28, 2026--Katie Pries has been named Country Executive for Northern Trust Asset Servicing in Canada, based in Toronto.
